data.description: Welcome to your new home in the charming Lakewood Park bird sanctuary community, where the beauty of nature surrounds you. Here, you'll discover scenic lakes, abundant wildlife, and inviting walking trails. The community offers a range of recreational amenities, including basketball and tennis courts, soccer and baseball fields, a community pool, playgrounds, picnic areas, and even a disc golf course. Step inside this delightful rustic farmhouse-inspired property, where a clean yet warm visual palette awaits. The spacious open-concept layout with vaulted ceilings sets the stage for comfortable living. The large island kitchen is a highlight, adorned with exquisite granite countertops. Its clever design includes a pass-through window with granite bar seating, seamlessly connecting the indoors to the outdoors - perfect for al fresco dining. The heart of this home is the expansive pool patio area, spanning over 1,000 sqft, adorned with a wood panel ceiling lanai. This luxurious space beckons you to entertain with family BBQs or simply unwind in your private retreat. The deck and pool were resurfaced in 2015, ensuring your enjoyment for years to come. Both the master bedroom and spare bedroom offer slider access to the patio, and the spare bathroom conveniently doubles as a cabana bath. The property boasts a metal roof and a pool cage with solar pool heater, ensuring durability and comfort. Inside, you'll find a bonus family den that provides additional living space ideal for formal dining, home office, or recreational area. Notable upgrades include a renovated spare bath, a water heater from 2015, and an AC system from 2017. A whole-house gas generator was installed in 2017 for added peace of mind, and the tile was updated in 2017. In 2018, insulation improvements were made, and a new water system was installed in 2019 with added RO filtration. With no strict HOA regulations and an added parking pad, this property welcomes your boat, RV, and other recreational toys - ideal for outdoor enthusiasts. Additionally, this home's great proximity to Vero Beach and the Fort Pierce jetty ensures easy access to boating, fishing, dining, and beachcombing. Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to make this inviting property your own and start creating unforgettable moments in your luxurious pool patio oasis.
